+ * Returns true if it IS a boundary (next token starts a new statement).
+ * Returns false if the expression continues (e.g. `}.method()`, `} = obj`, etc.)
+ *
+ * @param {string} source
+ * @param {number} afterPos - position right after the `}`
+ * @returns {boolean}
+ */
